ndition storage for all active domain faces.\n- dm (inout): Domain descriptor receiving thermal face-boundary arrays. Arguments Type Intent Optional Attributes Name type( t_domain ), intent(inout) :: dm public  subroutine update_fbcy_cc_flow_halo (fl, dm) Update pipe-axis halo values for flow variables stored around the y-axis centreline.\n- fl (inout): Flow variables whose cylindrical-axis halos are reconstructed.\n- dm (in): Domain and symmetry metadata for the pipe axis. Arguments Type Intent Optional Attributes Name type( t_flow ), intent(inout) :: fl type( t_domain ), intent(inout) :: dm public  subroutine update_fbcy_cc_thermo_halo (tm, dm) Update pipe-axis halo values for thermal variables.\n- tm (inout): Thermal variables whose cylindrical-axis halos are reconstructed.\n- dm (in): Domain and symmetry metadata for the pipe axis. Arguments Type Intent Optional Attributes Name type( t_thermo ), intent(inout) :: tm type( t_domain ), intent(inout) :: dm public  subroutine update_fbcy_cc_mhd_halo (mh, dm) Update pipe-axis halo values for MHD variables.\n- mh (inout): MHD variables whose cylindrical-axis halos are reconstructed.\n- dm (in): Domain and symmetry metadata for the pipe axis. Arguments Type Intent Optional Attributes Name type( t_mhd ), intent(inout) :: mh type( t_domain ), intent(in) :: dm public  subroutine axis_mirror_fbcy (var, pencil, fbcy, ksym, dtmp, is_odd, axis_mode, assign_axis_to_var, nr, opt_r, opt_dz, axis_rn_mode) Reconstruct or mirror a cylindrical field across the pipe centreline. Read more… Arguments Type Intent Optional Attributes Name real(kind=WP), intent(inout) :: var (:,:,:) integer, intent(in) :: pencil real(kind=WP), intent(inout) :: fbcy (:,:,:) integer, intent(in) :: ksym (:) type(DECOMP_INFO), intent(in) :: dtmp logical, intent(in), optional :: is_odd integer, intent(in), optional :: axis_mode logical, intent(in), optional :: assign_axis_to_var integer, intent(in), optional :: nr real(kind=WP), intent(in), optional :: opt_r (: